snippet.title: 2012 ESA North Central Branch Linnaean Games Finals
snippet.description: Entomology students from the University of Wisconsin take on the University of Nebraska in the 2012 Entomological Society of America's North Central Branch Linnaean Games Finals, held in Lincoln Nebraska, June 5, 2012. Both teams will compete in the National Linnaean Games this November in Knoxville, TN (see http://www.entsoc.org/entomology2012).
